{"type": "article", "id": 21612, "title": "如何在朋友圈合理炫耀春节生活？", "description": "目标是羡慕嫉妒恨，不是进黑名单哦。", "date": "2016-02-12T08:00:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6945, "name": "春节"}, {"id": 6475, "name": "朋友圈"}, {"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 264, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071348278LGQhWSBj1wDYFgi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><b>1. 所有人：刷屏需谨慎。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134813DC3Q9yWuJmTdcxR1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>2. 朋友圈大赛之美食。多发当地小吃。</b><b>注意品种多样化。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071348139MTOha3ECpPGHtv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73535156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>3. 不要只发吃的，注意拍人，拍摆设。</b><b>过年给老爸老妈的礼物不如带新餐具——正好方便拍照。</b> </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"> <b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134814e6UropMYzDtcWn8a.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>4. 挑一道复杂的菜跟拍记录全程，最好自己上。</b> </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"> <b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134815U2HwzxaKuL9qYGVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55272727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>5. 朋友圈大赛之自拍。</b><b>过年了别光晒自己，一切的重点是有爱的 family，自拍带上爸妈，别非凑齐九张图，挑最酷的一张，假装很随意。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713481556GH2pBrdSCVJ9te.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82291667\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>6. 花钱度假的可以多发，</b><b>尤其是去热带的。就拍一张短袖短裙晒太阳。身材好的就比基尼。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134816UgfmCsqt1SYbe5kz.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>7. 老同学聚会，朋友圈交集不多的，干脆每个人轮流脸最小拍照，各用一张。</b>  <b><br></b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713481703on1uiF9QxqKZaz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>8. 朋友圈大赛之鸡汤文。抒情别太长，别太多标点符号。额度不高，</b><b>七天</b><b>最好只有一两次。可以配一张爸妈卖萌合照。注意时机，假期开头几天比较合适，这时候大家容忍度最高。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134818l375LTcEt0ZaCUYD.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.438\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>9. 注意发文开头，建议用段子。“刚才成功被我爷爷鄙视了……”“话说我们中学曾有个吴彦祖……”看图/鸡汤看吐了，这种还是受欢迎的。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134819MOPa13E8FDWwuHTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68768769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>10. 朋友圈</b><b>大赛之</b><b>春晚吐槽。认真研究节目单，提前保存好图片。不要老家没 wifi 临时下载猴赛雷浪费流量。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134819As34lbcuaIYmPoDN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>11. 说到这，请提前购买流量包。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134820qNuQKGmdLAHx0jfC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure></div>\n<p><b>12. 朋友圈</b><b>大赛之</b><b>娱乐活动。项目注意多样化，不要除了打牌就是看电影要不就 KTV。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134820kelDZbBvOY7gqpsJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>13. 哪怕你去野湖溜个冰。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134821J9Kh4HoBvmxGuz5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.503125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>14. 要是能玩成这样你就赢了。</b></p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151014BZWgTXOm79Li1t8A.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"><b>15. 熊孩子和宠物适合上镜。长的萌的那种。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134821uiZCFGnx6JOyjYep.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54669704\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>16. 晒片单的，注意时髦度，奥斯卡入围名单中规中矩。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134822O0vcmJqCs1XERBh8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62642369\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>17. 晒书的，配文不要太严肃，可以“擦终于把这个看完了，结局太无语/还是没懂怎么破……”</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713482342YMad7GWnUctyRZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>18. 晒晒怀旧。童年美照，趣味作文。字太丑就算了。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134824DOAyhVZ8K4TR5CBq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><b>19. 不幸加班的，也能想办法晒晒。尤其是初五初六心情都不好，发个加班照片帮助大家高兴高兴。年三十就别晒了——显得你太惨。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071348243tqZI9DVA2kbLiKw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64351852\" data-format=\"GIF\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>20. 单身狗被问什么奇葩问题，就自己消化消化吧。除非你想被安排相亲。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134825rAZtjzIOi3pFLR2C.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\n        \n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>21. 假期长的/年假一起休的，记得提醒所有人，我还在家呢。</b><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134826zDQVENxfATh8YmGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n        \n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><b>22. 好了。你赢了——好有意义的假期。</b></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134827QlnvRhsDq0WMe61U.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63179916\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>\n\n\n\n\n"}